16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T00:23:00.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"470227580a6898cd04d4440bdb2022726ff982d2","tid":676812,"uid":51932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T00:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/l2Sqb2raeiZLVDFaU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl2Sqb2raeiZLVDFaU%2Fgiphy.gif&h=70431a8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80815ba444b9fe635286bbf6d247c7fa7425bc33","tid":676812,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T00:33:55.000Z","msg":"突發 五毛狗仲點有糧出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180525/bknint-20180525063358873-0525_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180525%2Fbknint-20180525063358873-0525_17011_001.html&d=uXFdhwHKVZg4YdekkMzJYfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=3a670cc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180525/bknint-20180525063358873-0525_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北韓官媒釋善意　指金正恩全力為特金會作準備<br />\n05月25日(五)<br />\n07:08更新06:33建立<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普突然宣布取消「特金會」，並警告已準備好採取軍事行動，令朝鮮半島局勢急轉直下。北韓官媒周五（25日）隨即釋出善意，指朝方仍希望和美國對話，領袖金正恩正集中籌備同特朗普的會面，又形容對於美方取消「特金會」感到極度遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n朝中社引述北韓副外長金桂冠指，特朗普的決定不符合國際期望，指北韓願意在任何時間及任何方式和美國會談。他續指，美國單方取消「特金會」，顯示美朝兩國之間的敵意仍深，雙方急需會面，化解敵對關係。<br />\n<br />\n金桂冠表示，金正恩正集中籌備同特朗普的會面：「我們（北韓）承諾會盡最大努力，以維持朝鮮半島乃至世界的和平及穩定。」"},{"pid":"e33610e105ef550836545ed058e72462376015d0","tid":676812,"uid":12367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80815ba444b9fe635286bbf6d247c7fa7425bc33","tid":676812,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T00:33:55.000Z","msg":"突發 五毛狗仲點有糧出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180525/bknint-20180525063358873-0525_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.